  "texts": [
    "GRPO directly estimates advantages from the intra-group reward distribution.",
    "The policy parameters are then updated to maximize the expected reward while simultaneously minimizing divergence from a reference policy, typically quantified through the KL divergence.",
    "By eliminating the need for a separate value network, GRPO offers a simplified yet effective alternative to traditional actor-critic methods such as PPO."
  ],
